#: home/templates/home/pricing.html:47
msgid ""
"Transparent pricing for multi-country payroll with region-specific support, "
"reporting, compliance, and employee self-service."
msgstr ""

#: home/templates/home/pricing.html:57
msgid ""
"Transparent pricing for global payroll with predictable per-employee monthly "
